  "description": "OBRIX through Mathematical Chain emphasizing Voronoi Shatter. OBRIX's ring modulation source (proc2Type=ring mod) creates metallic, inharmonic tones. Voronoi Shatter at Crystallize 0.72 and GrainSize 15ms fragments these inharmonic tones into geometric grain clusters — the mathematical tessellation of already-mathematical FM relationships. Entropy Cooler at Stability 0.4. Quantum Smear at Observation 0.35, Feedback 0.55. Attractor Drive minimal (Bifurcation 0.2). The Voronoi geometric patterning is applied to inharmonic spectral material — mathematical structure on mathematical dissonance.",
